snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past Four Swords – Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack
snippet.description:
Play two of Link’s classic adventures, including one with online multiplayer, in The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past Four Swords - Now available for the Game Boy Advance - Nintendo Switch Online + Expansion Pack library!

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
